DDL - Data Definition Language (Changes the Structure of Table ,  Uses the table keyword in writing commands eg -  create table table_name (id int) )
      Commands - CAD   ~  create    (creates a table)
                       ~  alter      (Modifies the attributes(column) of table)
                       ~  drop        (deletes the entire table)


DML - Data Manipulation Language (Changes the data of table , doesnt use table keyword eg - select * fromm table_name ; )
      Commands    ~ select        (use to fetch the Data from table)
                  ~ update        (use to update records)
                  ~ insert        (use to insert records in table)
                  ~ delete        (delete records)


DCL - Data Control Language (Controls the data)
      Commands    ~ grant
                  ~ revoke
